{"type":"message","id":"c3eebb7f","parentId":"e3ff67c9","timestamp":"2026-03-12T18:58:13.644Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] The endpoint did **not** return the simple top-level shape the wrapper expected.\n\n**Expected by the wrapper**\n```json\n{\n  \"prediction_label\": \"string\",\n  \"confidence\": 0.98\n}\n```\n\n**Actual output**\n```json\n{\n  \"status\": 200,\n  \"metadata\": {\n    \"name\": \"kidney_cancer_detection_model\",\n    \"type\": \"ai_tool.kidney-cancer-detection-model\",\n    \"run_id\": \"c5f6bdfef59349cd8fd98a53bd1dd0a2\",\n    \"workflow_name\": \"KidneyCancer_detection\",\n    \"workflow_type\": \"NodeType : ai-tool\",\n    \"workflow_id\": \"25\",\n    \"workflow_run_id\": \"b1a313fa376d4bbda379aba0aae18124\"\n  },\n  \"data\": {\n    \"tracking_data\": {\n      \"inference_time\": \"1.9161 s\",\n      \"perception\": [\n        {\n          \"image_path\": \"626130f7c71f6b9e651c76be/69a2020385d6df1b7ccc15ff/kidney_test2.jpeg\",\n          \"prediction_label\": \"kidney_tumor\",\n          \"prediction\": \"kidney_tumor\",\n          \"confidence\": 0.9999794960021973,\n          \"class_probs\": {\n            \"kidney_normal\": 2.0543020582408644e-05,\n            \"kidney_tumor\": 0.9999794960021973\n          }\n        }\n      ]\n    },\n    \"model_info\": {\n      \"model_folder\": \"kidney_model_v1\",\n      \"model_path\": \"/usr/src/app/src/models/kidney_cancer_model/kidney_model_v1\"\n    }\n  }\n}\n```\n\nSo I extracted the meaningful result from:\n- `data.tracking_data.perception[0].prediction_label`\n- `data.tracking_data.perception[0].confidence`\n\nIf you want, I can also patch the wrapper so it accepts this real response format cleanly.","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_02e4ce9b8b8a62770169b30cbd594c8191842cdc386234bd0e\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":10154,"output":455,